    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2201660/extras/c07bc7dc1122d80b7f68503a01f424aa.avif?t=1722451486\" width=616 height=162 /></span><br><strong>Marabundle </strong>is a collection of <strong>4 games</strong> by small Brazilian studios. One Bundle, four games: 1 hack n' slash action game! 1 co-op puzzle platformer; 1 collectible card game with &quot;slap and swap&quot; mechanics! 1 action shoot 'em up! All these 4 games in one single bundle!<br><br>Check the description of each game included in this bundle:<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2201660/extras/b23c088f3a002c6a9d494b7fe617831a.avif?t=1722451486\" width=616 height=80 /></span><br>On the street in your neighborhood, the biggest <strong>Bafo</strong> competition in history is taking place. Face powerful opponents in a <strong>turn based combat</strong> and <strong>collect all the cards</strong> to be known as the Grand Champion of Bafo.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2201660/extras/db5e6ef5829b869b275c42f6d161b306.avif?t=1722451486\" width=616 height=80 /></span><br>Smear the skies with pieces of alien spaceships in <strong>Dogfights in SLZ</strong>, an <strong>arcade shoot'em up</strong> with a challenging and addictive aerial combat game.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2201660/extras/ada4549f48925ef0c6891afaf1877e80.avif?t=1722451486\" width=616 height=80 /></span><br>Cross an unknown nation to escape a devastated and scarce place, seeking a land full of resources to bring rest and prosperity to its people,<br>who bet their very lives on your journey. Defeat monsters trying to stop you in a <strong>hack'n slash, procedurally generated</strong> game!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2201660/extras/a317ce357bd50aed061106144476723f.avif?t=1722451486\" width=616 height=80 /></span><br>Join a friend and travel through the state of Maranhão by train preventing it from stopping because of its broken wagons by solving small <strong>puzzles </strong>on this <strong>co-op platformer</strong> game",
